name: Okey-Ducky
description:
Let the rubber ducky fly to save kids!

You will love to make a long long line of duckies.

Dodge pipes and rescue small duckies!

Challenge your best record!

It is totally non-commercial app. Don't worry about annoying ads or in-app purchase.

You can also enjoy this game on these platforms.
